{"type": "article", "id": 21609, "title": "REDECKER 510504", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-01T01:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135508jYowSdBmODq5hpbH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>这是一把专门清洗百叶窗的刷子，来自德国一家有80年的历史做刷子的品牌REDECKER。把手是榉木，连接着 4 圈山羊毛的刷毛，可以插进三排百叶，一次刷过后它们的正反两面都被清洗过了，大大提高清理百叶窗的效率。是一个可以长久使用的工具。<a href=\"http://www.chloros.jp/shopdetail/000000005234/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135505gmUZW8k215IFf4R3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135505My7EXw18fYz3CHn0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135506aJC1QTYcNL6WSyKV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21501014\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135507UmWZtAqXu4TLd8rI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66909091\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135507xi8R4TIXl1KSLocn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66909091\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>\n\n"}